data.description: Appliances will be replaced/updated prior to closing!  Welcome to your cute condo in the heart of the vibrant Domain area in Austin!  Nestled within this coveted locale, this spacious 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom sanctuary is updated and ready for move-in.  In 2023, LVP wood-look flooring on the lower level, and plush carpet upstairs was installed.  Updated ½ bath downstairs for guests.  Walk upstairs to find two large bedrooms and a full bath upstairs.  Outside, enjoy a large storage closet and a private patio for your morning coffee or evening cocktails, and enjoy dining alfresco.  Enjoy nature and walks with the pup in the lovely shaded greenbelt directly behind the condo.  Easy access to world-class shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Embrace the convenience of the Domain area and make this one your own!  HOA fee includes trash, recycling, exterior insurance, front yard/common area maintenance, pool, and more!
